# FastAPI Portfolio Tracker

This project is a FastAPI application that tracks stock portfolios and calculates profit and annualized returns.

## Key Components

- [main.py](mdc:main.py) - Database configuration and application entry point
- [database.py](mdc:database.py) - Database connection setup
- [models.py](mdc:models.py) - SQLAlchemy database models for Portfolio, Holding, and StockPrice
- [schemas.py](mdc:schemas.py) - Pydantic models for request/response validation
- [router.py](mdc:router.py) - FastAPI route handlers for all endpoints
- [helpers.py](mdc:helpers.py) - Utility functions for fetching stock prices and calculating returns

## Main Features

- Portfolio creation and management
- Stock price fetching using yfinance
- Profit and annualized return calculations
- SQLite database for persistent storage
